highlights.text: “Lạ Lùng” by Vũ. has been on Top Songs Vietnam the longest, at 391 weeks straight.
“NGƯỜI NHƯ ANH XỨNG ĐÁNG CÔ ĐƠN” by ANH TRAI "SAY HI", Vũ Cát Tường, Karik, Negav, Ngô Kiến Huy, and Jey B is the highest new entry on Top Songs Vietnam at #19.
Vũ. has the most spots on Top Songs Vietnam. “bình yên” is the highest at #17.
“Không Thời Gian” by Dương Domic is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Vietnam, up 133 spots at #26.
